<h3>Fastest daytime route</h3>
<p>	From Terminal 1, go to the Kansai Airport Station (adjacent to the terminal).  Take a JR or Nankai line train to Rinku-Town Station (one stop).
The Kansai Airport Line (JR) or the Nankai Airport Line both run between Kansai Airport and Rinku Town.  ￼</p>
<p>Exit the station (follow signs for Exit 5), and the hotel is a short walk from Rinku-Town Station.</p>

<div class="highlight">
<strong>Tip:</strong> ICOCA and other IC cards work on all JR and Nankai trains at KIX. Scan out at Kansai Airport Station to exit toward the hotel.
</div>

